transcript.title: Visit of President Yudhoyono Address to Parliament
transcript.content:
To view the transcript of Prime Minister Kevin Rudd's welcoming address to President Susilo Bambang Yudhoyono and President Yudhoyono's address to a joint meeting of the Australian houses of parliament, see pages 2133-2142 of the Hansard report.

(The video related to this transcript is available from the Multimedia section of this website.)
